{"tid":2425161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登回應空襲敘利亞 要伊朗「自求多福」","createTime":"2021-02-27T07:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T08:37:39.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9e0c16ab1561462d0b335ab43e4d51c49dd21464","tid":2425161,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:05:19.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美總統拜登當地時間25日，下令空襲敘利亞境內親伊朗民兵組織，是他上任後首次發動軍事打擊。拜登事後向伊朗發出警告，要他們自求多福。<br />\n<br />\n拜登當地時間週五赴德州視察暴風雪災情時，被記者問到對敘利亞的空襲意在傳達什麼樣的訊息？拜登回應，「你們的行為不可能沒有後果，小心點吧。」<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3451196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3451196&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEmwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=74028901\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3451196&h=b903e466\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3451196</a>"},{"pid":"6af302dab384451e028b32f13cff8497ac23634a","tid":2425161,"uid":156652,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJfqQRD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJfqQRD.gif&h=72d658c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dd0e02ae4f54e2f771c8bef2010523220e60e32","tid":2425161,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QJUWc5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQJUWc5d.jpg&h=97e218aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9d83d0eaed5a306f821e43d8dd5fbe38cc6e266","tid":2425161,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:15:30.000Z","msg":"對住牙習咪又係奶袋底<br />\n收皮啦紅登<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a5c89c5ff8f27fa039bd03175d858cfe003b3e","tid":2425161,"uid":115579,"like":1,"disli